Trade/Device Name(s): In Vitro Nano-Check™ AMI cTnI Cardiac Marker Test
Regulation Name(s): Creatine phosphokinase/creatine kinase or isoenzymes test system
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for In Vitro Nano-Check AMI cTnI rapid immunoassay for cardiac marker detection in serum and plasma
Indications for Use Summary: Qualitative determination of cardiac troponin I (cTnI) in human serum and plasma to aid in the diagnosis of acute myocardial infarction (AMI)
